'''''Firethorn''''' was a frigate in the [[Galactic Alliance Defense Fleet]]. It was stationed at [[Toryaz Station]] during the [[Corellian/Legends|Corellian]]-[[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] negotiations in [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]] to protect the [[Narsacc Habitat]].

